<td valign=middle align=left>
The Lab for Interactive Artificial Intelligence is mostly made up of <font color="#ff8811"><b>the pfunk
research group</b></font>, a diverse group of researchers and
researchers-in-training. Our backgrounds range from systems to
cognitive science to algorithmic machine learning to good old
fashioned AI and several places outside and in between. The <b>p</b>
in pfunk stands for <b>p</b>robablistic. As for the funk, it stands
for many things, as well it should. Specific interpretations are left
as an exercise for the reader. 
